data.description: This spectacular 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom lakefront home is located in the prominent and highly sought after Waters Edge neighborhood. The stunning kitchen features beautiful granite countertops, sleek stainless steel appliances and upgraded cabinets. You'll appreciate the open floorplan with an abundance of natural lighting and gorgeous hardwood floors. The split bedroom layout provides extra privacy for the master suite. The amazing master bathroom has his and her sinks, a walk-in shower and a walk-in closet. You will also appreciate the screened-in lanai overlooking your fenced backyard with breathtaking views of the lake. This residence is located near top rated schools, shopping, restaurants, golf courses and the world's most famous beach. Call to schedule an appointment today!
